title: I GOT RIPPED OFF! the joom app: MY TINY POINT OF VIEW | WE DEEM
excerpt: What is the Joom App you ask? Well, it is pretty similar to the Wish app or geek and somewhat similar to AliExpress. It is an online Chinese market where you...
description:
What is the Joom App you ask? Well, it is pretty similar to the Wish app or geek and somewhat similar to AliExpress. It is an online Chinese market where you purchase cheap Chinese products and have them shipped to your country. 

I decided to give it a chance and order a Nintendo Switch Keyboard. Unfortunately, instead of getting the product, I received a sticker and pretty much an empty envelope. I tried contacting the Joom app customer service but it was a horrible experience and I have got nowhere as you will see in the video.  

Don’t forget to follow the We Deem Channel on Instagram to see the gaming collection: https://www.instagram.com/wedeemchannel/
